snippet.title: Sulfur - Official Demo Update Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the latest Sulfur trailer for the upcoming action-adventure game, which combines FPS mechanics with RPG elements. It's up to you to survive brutal encounters with enemies and make important decisions to outsmart them.

Sulfur has a planned release date of 2024 on PC (Steam). The Sulfur demo is available to play now.
